{"id":232369680,"title":"《群眾觀點》環保餐具集資產品使用情況問卷調查","content":"http://i.imgur.com/Q8eukly.jpg\n\n各位無痕生活版的版友，大家好。我是網路媒體《群眾觀點》的編輯。\n「在集資平台上買了那麼多食物袋、環保杯、環保吸管，大家真的有在用嗎？」相信很多人都有過這樣的疑問。\n\n專門報導群眾集資產業的媒體《群眾觀點》，將在近期發起報導專題，探討台灣這2-3年來的環保食器集資風潮。 從 2017 年的食物袋開始，到近期的各種飲料杯和環保吸管，環保餐具在台灣的集資金額屢創新高。熱烈下單過後，這些產品的使用狀況究竟如何呢？為了探討這個問題，我們需要你的經驗分享，請大家幫忙填寫以下這份問卷。\n\n問卷只有 7 題，不到 3 分鐘就能填完，問卷結果將會是報導的重要素材，麻煩大家幫忙了！\n\n🌟問卷連結：https://crowd-funding.typeform.com/to/QBwZoQ\n\n大家若對此議題有任何想法，也歡迎留言告訴我。","excerpt":"各位無痕生活版的版友，大家好。我是網路媒體《群眾觀點》的編輯。「在集資平台上買了那麼多食物袋、環保杯、環保吸管，大家真的有在用嗎？」相信很多人都有過這樣的疑問。專門報導群眾集資產業的媒體《群眾觀點》，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-25T07:47:56.834Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-25T07:53:17.301Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":21,"tags":[],"topics":["無痕飲食","減塑","環保杯","不鏽鋼吸管","環保"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"Ellie","department":"ellie17","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":20},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/Q8eukly.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"3c4b5970-93ae-4e72-bba1-621fc4340857","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Q8euklyl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/Q8euklyl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Q8euklyl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-25T07:53:17.301Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-25T07:53:17.301Z"},{"id":"3c4b5970-93ae-4e72-bba1-621fc4340857","url":"http://i.imgur.com/Q8eukly.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/Q8eukly","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Q8euklyl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"20